        <Parent_String>Eastern European Upper Paleolithic styles and periods [300106795], European Upper Paleolithic styles and periods [300106791], ancient European styles and periods [300019281], Early Western World [300019255], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
